      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1898_AS_RBH_1_00021"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Richard
                     Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb190427" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">I. Wollzeile 15</hi></rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1898_AS_RBH_1_00022"/><salute>Lieber Richard,</salute> Sie werden die Rechnung<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chon kriegen!</p><p>Ich war auf dem <rs ref="#pmb189" type="place">Semmering</rs>.</p><p>Gehen Sie vielleicht <date>Sam<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date> zur <rs ref="#pmb30593" type="work">Braut
                  von Me<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ina</rs>?</p><p>Oder für Freitag im <rs ref="#pmb819" type="place">Pucher</rs>?</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr <signed>Arth</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
